title: Texas serial bomber suspect dead
text:
Texas serial bomber suspect dead 8:04pm IST - 01:21 
A 24-year-old man suspected of a series of deadly bombings around Austin, Texas, blew himself up early on Wednesday as police closed in on him, police officials said. Rough Cut (no reporter narration). ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
